```

### 前端测试 — loadRun 填充 professionTokens


```typescript
describe('Cost Breakdown — professionTokens from historical run', () => {
  // T22.7: loadRun 从 API 响应填充 professionTokens
  it('should populate professionTokens from API response', async () => {
    // Mock: { ..., profession_tokens: { architect: 12000, coder: 8500 } }
    // Call loadRun(id)
    // Assert: professionTokens.value deep equals { architect: 12000, coder: 8500 }
  })

  // T22.8: 空 profession_tokens 清空 ref
